  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This emergency project (with $500K in support from BMGF) will:
-Provide humanitarian assistance to the affected population of the northern coast of Peru due to the flooding and destruction caused by the rainfall of El Ni&#xF1;o. 

Objectives 
- Support the affected population of La Libertad and Piura by implementing cash for work activities to recovery beneficiary livelihoods and irrigation canal. 
-Support the affected population of La Libertad and Piura by implementing a cash voucher system for the distribution of school kits to support the reintegration of children in school.</narrative>
  </description>
